tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE OrderBook (
    OrderID UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    Symbol VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    Price DECIMAL NOT NULL,
    Quantity INT NOT NULL,
    Timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
)

CREATE TABLE OrderBook (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_id INT,
    order_type VARCHAR(20),
    order_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    order_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE MarketDepth (
    depth_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    instrument_id INT,
    bid_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    bid_quantity INT,
    ask_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    ask_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE market_depth (
  symbol VARCHAR(50) PRIMARY KEY,
  bid_price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  bid_quantity INT NOT NULL,
  ask_price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  ask_quantity INT NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
  trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  symbol VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
  trade_price DECIMAL(10, 2) NOT NULL,
  trade_quantity INT NOT NULL,
  timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE order_book (
    order_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    order_type VARCHAR(255),
    order_price DECIMAL,
    order_quantity INT,
    participant_id INT
);

CREATE TABLE trade_history (
    trade_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    buy_order_id INT,
    sell_order_id INT,
    quantity_traded INT,
    trade_price DECIMAL,
    trade_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE orders (
    order_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    participant_id UUID NOT NULL,
    order_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    order_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    order_quantity INT,
    order_timestamp TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE market_data (
    data_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    data_timestamp TIMESTAMP NOT NULL,
    trade_type VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    trade_price DECIMAL(10, 2),
    trade_quantity INT
);

CREATE TABLE market_depth (
    depth_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    data_id UUID NOT NULL,
    depth_level INT,
    offers_quantity INT,
    bids_quantity INT,
    FOREIGN KEY (data_id) REFERENCES market_data(data_id)
);
